    "description": "Titanium alloy elastic modulus was varied ±10% around the nominal 114 GPa and UHMWPE block modulus was varied ±15%; construct stiffness QoI changed by less than 4% across all perturbations. Pedicle screw–rod interface contact stiffness was swept across one order of magnitude; yield force QoI varied by less than 6%, confirming that simulation outputs are robust to plausible material and contact uncertainty within the ASTM F1717 test configuration."
  },
